-- Turkish Isbank obtains $250 mln securitisation loan
-- By Dasha Afanasieva
-- Thu Dec 11, 2014 02:41AM EST
-- None



ISTANBUL, Dec 11 (Reuters) - Turkish lender Isbank <ISCTR.IS> obtained a $250 million securitisation loan which will be used for the financing needs of small and medium-sized companies, the company said in a filing to the Istanbul stock exchange on Thursday.   (Reporting by Dasha Afanasieva; Editing by Daren Butler)  ((dasha.afanasieva@thomsonreuters.com; +90 212 350 7051;))  Keywords: ISBANK SECURITISATION/

